WEBVTT

00:06.000 --> 00:08.080
Are you all right, dear?

00:08.080 --> 00:09.519
Just a little nervous.

00:12.480 --> 00:15.720
Now, you're sure you still want to
go through with it?

00:15.720 --> 00:17.160
Yes...

00:17.160 --> 00:18.559
..it's what I want.

00:25.920 --> 00:27.199
Open up, it's the police!

00:28.120 --> 00:31.000
"Were there brought unto him
little children,

00:31.000 --> 00:33.000
"that he should put his hands
on them and pray.

00:33.000 --> 00:35.079
"And the disciples rebuked them.

00:35.079 --> 00:39.079
"But Jesus said, 'Suffer little
children and forbid them not to

00:39.079 --> 00:42.399
" 'come unto me, for of such is the
kingdom of heaven.'

00:42.399 --> 00:44.840
"The Lord has made clear his love
for all of us..." Maude!

00:44.840 --> 00:46.719
Don't worry, they haven't got any
evidence.

00:46.719 --> 00:49.679
On the contrary. I've persuaded a
couple of your victims to confess.

00:49.679 --> 00:51.399
They're not victims.
It's a woman's right

00:51.399 --> 00:52.719
what she does with her own body!

00:52.719 --> 00:55.359
Well, it appears the thought of
eternal damnation is stronger

00:55.359 --> 00:57.280
than your left-wing propaganda.

00:57.280 --> 00:59.200
You mean you've put the fear
of God into them!

00:59.200 --> 01:00.719
She could go down for years!

01:00.719 --> 01:03.200
Back off! Back off!

01:03.200 --> 01:05.120
Or I'll arrest you, as well.

01:05.120 --> 01:06.400
Get off.

01:06.400 --> 01:09.079
You're a dead man! Do you hear me?!

01:09.079 --> 01:10.120
Dead!

